The FWM Magazine belongs to Fashion World Models, an exclusive network of photographers and photographic models. Once again, FWM Magazine promotes our members and highlights international models and photographers. In this edition we introduce you Patricia Andrade, besides being a great professional, is a model with a rare beauty. Former Miss Brazil and current television presenter, photographed for FWM in a paradisiacal beach. Carola Varini former playmate, photographed in Milan for FWM, representing the Italian beauty. Kandie Justine a U.S. model enchants with its beauty. Kristal Ann from Canada. Two models of South Carolina, Chelsea Cothran and Kaitlynn Lewis, two young very talented. Finally two works of photographers Liliana Pinho from Portugal and Gabriele Ardemagni from Italy, two fantastic works. We hope you enjoy!
